4.Temparature of a city in fahernheit degrees is input through the keyboard.write a program to convert this temparature into centigrade degrees.

PROGRAM:
      #include <stdio.h>
int main()
{
    float f,c;
    printf("Enter the temparature : ");
    scanf("%f",&f);
    c=(f - 32)*(5.0,9.0);
    printf("\nResult : %f",c);
    return 0;
} 
---- OUTPUT ----
Enter the temparature : 100

Result : 37.7778

